  "description": {
    "de": "Der verrückte Erfinder Stek Dardar soll diese seltsamen und äußerst gefährlichen Messer bestellt haben. Niemand wußte wozu, bis er eines Tages seinem Gott einen riesigen Haufen blutigen Fleisches opferte.",
    "en": "One day, the infamously crazy T. Bun Stek found two strange yet impressive knives... No one could figure out what they were for. He used the very same knives to sacrifice half his livestock to the Gods and soon after they bellowed the answer from the heave's. He was slaughtering a particularly noisy cow at that very moment... The poor guy didn't hear a word.",
    "es": "El ilustre loco Stek Rokefor encargó hacer estos extraños y temibles cuchillos. Nadie sabía para qué servían hasta que intentó regalar comida a su dios.",
    "fr": "L'illustre fou Stek Dardar aurait commandé ces couteaux étranges et redoutables. Nul n'en connaissait l'utilité jusqu'à ce qu'il tente d'offrir à manger à son dieu.",
    "id": "49202",
    "pt": "Estas facas estranhas e terríveis aparentemente pertenceram ao famoso louco Stek Dardar. Seu uso foi descoberto quando ele sacrificou carne para seu deus."
  },
